groupBy([#DataSource], function=count())
| sort(_count, order=desc)
| limit(50)

---

Discover All Repositories and Data Sources
cqlgroupBy([#repo, #data_source_name], function=count())
| sort(_count, order=desc)
| limit(100)


Find Vulnerability / Spotlight Data Specifically
#data_source_name = /spotlight|vuln|exposure/i
| groupBy([#data_source_name, #event_simpleName], function=count())
| sort(_count, order=desc)

Find Any CVE References Across All Repos
#repo = *
| CVE_ID = *
| groupBy([#repo, #data_source_name, #event_simpleName], function=count())
| sort(_count, order=desc)
| limit(50)

If empty CVE,
#repo = *
